分，幫助發酵過程做得更好<br />\n昆蟲蘊含豐富蛋白質，發酵成為氨基酸，為蔗汁添加營養<br />\n有研究指出發酵食品營養價值更高，更有利人體吸收<br />\n蔗汁檔主真係宅心仁厚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;"},{"pid":"4ba8bba50fbfd8399e2c1d4168237368497b0aeb","tid":617604,"uid":18521,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:44:53.000Z","msg":"加糖水未加糖水囉<br />\n<br />\n點解又要有死蟲又要有異味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保管好少少都唔係咁難姐下資"},{"pid":"fa09c356c8812cfb8c9d41bb9c5ea3b90a57aeae","tid":617604,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"支那，仲要街攤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60de64dd301d0c381d9231be66d557f44585b690","tid":617604,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"咁都抽到耶撚水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca71f28830c97ead5e0d616bac6d0b5a36c78452","tid":617604,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"琴日老豆先買左4支返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話好抵好正 我都飲左半枝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9c0f6149c3c3c7ed876212bbfb7c8df625ed89","tid":617604,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223b057922dd320108bddf3eaa3f5a7d54d57c82","tid":617604,"uid":90863,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"返大陸住啦<br />\n大灣區光榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36dc11300b2819578ccd974c06f5f54c9605c4cf","tid":617604,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re