By":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"其實佢呢D生意仔偷工減料慳得幾多啊?"},{"pid":"e1b4a3e924af2669a346f2cdd532e0043e80e317","tid":617604,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39f3cccaa84fc2e95d2206744dadb9a7972d56de","tid":617604,"uid":392,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T02:03:20.000Z","msg":"琴日好似仲有單牛肉麵定咩俾行家玩屎<br />\n真係痴撚線國家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180405/58028419\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F58028419&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0Ljl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=3a2d8920\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180405%2F58028419&h=7461e5ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180405/58028419</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6310df7b0a6157c98591c22a4549f27e24709eee","tid":617604,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聖經中有五餅二魚的故事，內地蔗汁檔竟也發生類似事件，真相卻令人震驚。內地傳媒報道，深圳執法人員近日巡查時，發現有現榨甘蔗汁的攤販，只以1根甘蔗榨出5杯甘蔗汁，上前了解，發現原來榨汁機暗藏喉管連接發泡膠箱，當中載着渾濁發臭兼有死蟲的糖<span style=\"color: red;\">清液</span>體<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n據報道，深圳執法人員近日在深圳保安區婦幼保健院路段巡查時，發現有蔗汁攤檔生意不俗，惟仔細觀察卻見檔主只榨一根甘蔗，竟能榨出5杯蔗汁，大感奇怪遂上前查看。結果拆開榨汁機後，發現旁邊木板下藏了一發泡膠箱，兩者以喉管連接，並設有水泵。<br />\n<br />\n執法人員打開發泡膠箱，即飄出異味；仔細看，當中泛黃液體不單渾濁，更藏有不少死蟲。經了解下原來箱中為混入糖精的糖水，檔主售賣時會自行控制榨汁機的兩個開關掣，邊榨汁邊混入糖水，以降低成本。<br />\n<br />\n深圳寶安區新安街道執法隊稱，該名無良攤販常在區內開檔，多次被查處發現以違法行為降低成本，罔顧消費者健康，多次被揭發卻仍不改善，提醒大眾在街頭幫襯時，需要警惕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180404/s00004/1522811677946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180404%2Fs00004%2F1522811677946&d=8%2BmwyUVWATMUob%2FDox0Ljl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=05b09382\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180404%2Fs00004%2F1522811677946&h=7c07e79d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180404/s00004/1522811677946</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9db56b496d9110c8588a3405c9de313289db67dd","tid":617604,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7dbab637ef6438d8b20941c17b4e1d091d997551","tid":617604,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:19:19.000Z","msg":"其實佢呢D生意仔偷工減料慳得幾多啊?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:31:33.000Z","msg":"工廠都用工業鹽比員工食喇 <br />\n差幾蚊都要賺到盡"},{"pid":"fb104d22c3c544ad5ac048255f144a31ea87f465","tid":617604,"uid":14244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ebeac9f6a5601d86f2e9cadf59054bfbbebfdc","tid":617604,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"349256d8ad6fe4896eb721f0a3735af3b21d4810","tid":617604,"uid":83328,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T08:24:57.000Z","msg":"五餅二魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"真係幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74e017cc468566a62bf0bda2f77ebc989dc983f","tid":617604,"uid":116289,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"肥料摻了金坷垃，一袋能頂兩袋撒！"},{"pid":"6682bb1fa8aca5cb6918c35b17d455